  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-04 drift specimen)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package contains a targeted W-AR-04 weakness: the primary ValidationResult was generated under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-24q3-build-2 (modelVersion 2024-q3-build-2) whereas the UnitOfAssurance declares currentModelVersion 2026-q1-build-7, representing a multi-year version drift that invalidates the supporting evidence.",
